peril.model.board.links

Class ModelLink

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • peril.model.board.links.ModelLink

  • public final class ModelLink
extends java.util.Observable
    Encapsulates the behaviour of a link between two ModelCountrys. This link can have multiple states.
    Since:
    2018-03-16
    Version:
    1.01.04
    Author:
    Joshua_Eddy
